side."

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "cardhead649" <cardhead649@y...> wrote:
> Empath chuckles.  "Slight case of acrophobia, Night Shade?"
> 
> Reaching the shore, the Seeker makes a gentle landing on the 
beach.  
> "Last stop, everyone off."
> 
> OOC: For those of you who aren't into psychology, acrophobia is 
fear 
> of heights.
>
